title: HINSLEAMER 10.3” Magnetic Drawing Board for Kids Toddlers, Magnetic Dot Art, Doodle Board with Pen & Beads, Montessori Educational Preschool Toy for Ages 3 4 5 6 Boys Girls (Medium Yellow Duck)
description: Feature: Colorful Magnetic Drawing Board This magnetic drawing board has a cute appearance and colorful beads, which will easily attract children's attention. Fully sealed design: The magnetic drawing board is made of high-quality acrylic material and a fully enclosed design, you will no longer worry about beads being lost or swallowed by children. Portable and lightweight: Our magnetic drawing board can be easily put into a backpack and carried anywhere, whether it is on a trip, restaurant or going out, children can enjoy their creative time. Multipurpose toy: Colored magnetic beads can be used as color cognition teaching aids, and can also be used to teach counting; At the same time, It can exercise children's attention, imagination and hand control ability.
feature_bullets: [" 【Interesting Magnetic Drawing Board】:The magnetic drawing board contains colorful magnetic beads, which are cute in shape, and children will soon be attracted by this doodle board. Let kids enjoy their hours of “drawing” time."," 【Easy to Play & Create as You Like】: Insert the patterned card, Children use the magnetic pen to pick up brightly colored beads into the corresponding positions under the guidance of the pattern. Or children can freely draw on the drawing board as their desired patterns."," 【Friendly to Kids & Durable】: The magnetic dot-to-dot drawing board is made of friendly ABS plastic material, smooth surface, fully sealed acrylic panel box designed, and can effectively avoid the risk of lost and swallowed beads."," 【Excellent Educational Toy】: This magnetic drawing board is a perfect educational tool for teaching children to learn colors, shapes, and counting, which can improve children's imagination, fine motor skills, hand-eye coordination and keep focus."," 【Great Gift for Kids】: This magnetic drawing board measures 10.3\" *9.6\", comes with 6 double-sided cards and provides 12 patterns. You can easily put it in the backpack and take it anywhere wants, such as for travel, long car drives & airplane activities, your kids will be busy on this magnetic game and keep quiet. This learning and educational preschool toy is the perfect gift for toddler girls boys aged 3 4 5 6."]
